{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and that's why we had cucumbers, and we had some vegetables, because I grew them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyhow, my father-- my father was killed during the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] clean-up, or whatever they call it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not [NON-ENGLISH], during the-- the [? thing ?] of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened in-- in the morning, my father went out, I guess to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was the thing-- to get up and to go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came running back home and said to my mother, take the children and go to these people-- to these Polish or Ukrainian people-- and stay with them, because I think there's going to be-- it looks like today there's going to be an aktion here.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm going to see what's going on, and I'll follow you there and I'll meet you there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my-- my mother took me and my sister, just one light coat-- I remember like today-- a little grey coat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister was born in 1937, so she was-- she was five younger than me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was like five years old at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we ran to these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We somehow got out and ran to these people and knocked at their doors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And naturally, nobody opened the doors for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and at that time already was a lot of tumult there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot of going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- she turned around from there and started just going ahead of herself, you know, just not knowing where she was going or what was going on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, she saw like a little potato-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It looked like a dog's house, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
